Package auto

Class SelescriptBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • auto.SelescriptBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SelescriptListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SSBaseListener
    public class SelescriptBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements SelescriptListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of SelescriptListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
